---
title: Pecan-Crusted Roasted Salmon with Maple Sweet Potato Mash and Brussels Sprouts
description: Making pecan-crusted crispy salmon is surprisingly quick and easy when you follow our few simple steps! Your final product will be savoury, crunchy salmon fillets with a smooth maple sweet potato mash and flavour-packed Brussels sprouts alongside.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/saumon-roti-en-croute-de-pacanes-a62dfc79.jpg
